trailingComments.value: * * Returns an Observable that emits only the last item emitted by the source Observable. * It optionally takes a predicate function as a parameter, in which case, rather than emitting * the last item from the source Observable, the resulting Observable will emit the last item * from the source Observable that satisfies the predicate. * * * * @param {function} predicate - the condition any source emitted item has to satisfy. * @return {Observable} an Observable that emits only the last item satisfying the given condition * from the source, or an NoSuchElementException if no such items are emitted. * @throws - Throws if no items that match the predicate are emitted by the source Observable. * @method last * @owner Observable
